### Which @angular/* package(s) are relevant/related to the feature request?

core

### Description

It would be useful have globalSignal primitive. This would reduce boilerplate as well which currently needs services to maintain state.

### Proposed solution

```
export class ComponentA {
  foo = globalSignal<string>('some-unique-identifier-string', 'default-value');
}

export class ComponentB {
  // This should have the value already if there was a globalSignal with the same identifier with value set
  foo = globalSignal<string>('some-unique-identifier-string');

  onClick() {
    // this should update the all the globalSignal references with the same identifier from all non-destroyed components 
    foo.set('change');
  }
}
```

### Alternatives considered

Having a signal in a service and inject it and share the variables among components

